With each member bringing a unique set of influences, Frigs creates a sound that is hard to pin down and an impression that's unshakable. Led by the force of Bria's vocals, the band has earned a reputation for putting on an hypnotic and visceral live performance. Embracing the mercurial and experimental, their shows are built upon instinct; a vocal growl can unexpectedly give way to a hushed whisper; languid drones boil over into guttural and searing tones.
